Maaf?

524
00:37:42,052 --> 00:37:44,979
Maaf, bisakah anda...

525
00:37:47,349 --> 00:37:50,610
Bisakah anda memberi tahu saya
apa yang diwakili huruf itu?

526
00:37:50,727 --> 00:37:52,353
Hanya berarti
reserved* (dipesan).

527
00:37:52,354 --> 00:37:54,480
Ini adalah tempat
parkir layanan sosial.

528
00:37:54,481 --> 00:37:56,357
Tempat itu dipesan untuk
salah satu manajer.

529
00:37:56,358 --> 00:37:58,993
Tentu saja. Dipesan.

530
00:37:59,778 --> 00:38:01,954
Terima kasih.

531
00:38:11,081 --> 00:38:12,665
Oh.

532
00:38:12,666 --> 00:38:15,218
Oh, anjrit. Anjrit.

533
00:38:16,712 --> 00:38:18,721
Terima kasih.

534
00:38:19,673 --> 00:38:21,090
Anjrit, anjrit.

